
  C H A N G E L O G
  =================

  This file summarizes *all* types of changes to the MP4H sources,
  i.e. changes between each patchlevel (1.x.y->1.x.(y+1) and
  1.x.y->1.(x+1).0). Take this logfile for concrete and detailed
  information about every single change.
  ___________________________________________________________________________

  Changes between 0.5.5 and SNAP:

    *) Rearranging documentation hierarchy (06-Feb-2000):
       In order to write documentation, i firstly write it in French,
       translations in english should follow soon.  This implies some
       changes in file hierarchy.
       [Denis Barbier]

    *) Add verbatim inclusion of files (06-Feb-2000):
       [Denis Barbier]

    *) Internal changes in src/builtin.c (06-Feb-2000):
       These changes are made to fix some minor problems and to clean up
       source code.
       [Denis Barbier]

  Changes between 0.5.4 and 0.5.5:

    *) Fix ``whitespace=delete'' attribute (30-Jan-2000):
       [Denis Barbier]

  Changes between 0.5.3 and 0.5.4:

    *) Documentation available in POD format (06-Dec-1999):
       [Denis Barbier]

    *) Add ``singleline'' attribute (06-Dec-1999):
       This attribute changes the behavior of <subst-in-string> and
       <subst-in-var>.  By default, ^ matches an empty string after a
       newline and $ an empty string before a newline.  When this
       attribute is set, ^ only matches the beginning of the string 
       and $ the end.
       [Denis Barbier]

  mp4h 0.5.3 (30-Nov-1999):
    First public release.
